    {
        "content": "<p>At <a href=\"https://fosdem.org/2025/\">FOSDEM 2025</a> Miguel held a Keynote about <a href=\"https://fosdem.org/2025/schedule/event/fosdem-2025-6507-rust-for-linux/\">Rust for Linux</a>. The <a href=\"https://video.fosdem.org/2025/\">video recordings</a> are still being processed and not available yet. But the <a href=\"https://fosdem.org/2025/events/attachments/fosdem-2025-6507-rust-for-linux/slides/235707/2025-02-0_iwSaMYM.pdf\">slides</a> are available and have a nice summary of Miguel's community survey.</p>\n<p>The popular German news site Heise has an <a href=\"https://www.heise.de/en/news/FOSDEM-25-Confidence-in-Rust-for-the-Linux-kernel-10267067.html\">article</a> about that as well.</p>\n<p><span class=\"user-mention\" data-user-id=\"411477\">@Miguel Ojeda</span> Thanks! <span aria-label=\"+1\" class=\"emoji emoji-1f44d\" role=\"img\" title=\"+1\">:+1:</span></p>",
        "id": 497596335,
        "sender_full_name": "Dirk Behme",
        "timestamp": 1738653270
    },
    {
        "content": "<p><span class=\"user-mention silent\" data-user-id=\"669329\">Dirk Behme</span> <a href=\"#narrow/channel/293929-Announcements/topic/Other.20articles.20and.20posts/near/497596335\">said</a>:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>At <a href=\"https://fosdem.org/2025/\">FOSDEM 2025</a> Miguel held a Keynote about <a href=\"https://fosdem.org/2025/schedule/event/fosdem-2025-6507-rust-for-linux/\">Rust for Linux</a>. The <a href=\"https://video.fosdem.org/2025/\">video recordings</a> are still being processed and not available yet. But the <a href=\"https://fosdem.org/2025/events/attachments/fosdem-2025-6507-rust-for-linux/slides/235707/2025-02-0_iwSaMYM.pdf\">slides</a> are available and have a nice summary of Miguel's community survey.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>Meanwhile the <a href=\"https://video.fosdem.org/2025/janson/fosdem-2025-6507-rust-for-linux.mp4\">video recording</a> is available. Please note that in the first ~10min they had issues with presenting the slides (it was the same in the live stream). And it seems the direct link to the <a href=\"https://fosdem.org/2025/events/attachments/fosdem-2025-6507-rust-for-linux/slides/236835/2025-02-0_iwSaMYM.pdf\">slides</a> has changed since my post above (hopefully this one stays now).</p>\n<div class=\"message_inline_image message_inline_video\"><a href=\"https://video.fosdem.org/2025/janson/fosdem-2025-6507-rust-for-linux.mp4\" title=\"video recording\"><video preload=\"metadata\" src=\"https://uploads.zulipusercontent.net/b7e7f9940409d0ada03835b8ee36f232a70e2cce/68747470733a2f2f766964656f2e666f7364656d2e6f72672f323032352f6a616e736f6e2f666f7364656d2d323032352d363530372d727573742d666f722d6c696e75782e6d7034\"></video></a></div>",
        "id": 499080791,
        "sender_full_name": "Dirk Behme",
        "timestamp": 1739301133
    },
